?We are moving further away from the 2030 Agenda [for sustainable developme=
nt],? said Luca De Fraia of ActionAid Italy. ?Not only are we missing the t=
arget in terms of quantity, but also the quality of aid is lagging behind.?

Despite a marginal rise in aid going to the least developed countries (from=
 0.11% in 2017 to 0.12% in 2018), 16 countries, among the poorest in the wo=
